data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!  Come take a look at this great home that boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a den and has almost 2,000 sq ft of living space!  The kitchen comes with all appliances and has a pantry for storage.  There is a breakfast bar as well as a dining area.  The living room has sliding glass doors that lead out to the large, screened lanai and the master bedroom has a French door that accesses the Lanai as well.  The master bath has separate tub and shower and dual sinks.  There is an added feature of a built-in desk adjacent to the kitchen.  The den is perfect for anyone who works from home, as it has double French doors that can be closed for privacy.  Luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home with the exception of one bedroom, which has carpet, and the bathrooms which have tile.  But wait, there's more...the back and sides of the yard are fully fenced with wooden privacy fence and there is a fully permitted shed in the back for extra storage!  BONUS...the home is getting a brand-new roof as well.  Don't delay...schedule your showing today!!
